Single Parent Household

Makes up a small portion of the household (how much?)

As a group takes the most advantage of discounts. page 12

Sales of produce is disappointing low. page 13

Large majority of the demographic live in households with yearly income less than $50k. page 15

As a specific grocery item, produce is the segement that sees more of the marketing campaign. page 17

13 and 18 are the most ambitious marketing campaigns, involving 20 or more departments. page 18

produce also happens to be the department where we see large amount of sales for a small discount. page 20

Different commodities yield different result for same amount of discount. eg. beef, frozen and diapers and disposables need little discount to produce large amount of sale. page 22
